            <p>I started working in a Research & Development laboratory at Egis. This laboratory uses solid-state analysis techniques such as <a href = "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QHMzFUo0NL8">X-ray Powder Diffraction</a>, <a href = "https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s40828-015-0008-y">Thermal Analysis</a>, or <a href = "https://www.nexus-analytics.com.my/how-does-laser-diffraction-work/">Laser-Diffraction</a> to determine and improve the properties of drugs.</p>
